  "synopsis": "For most high elves, the stillness of the Great Pulha Woodlands is paradise. For Acer, it's been 120 years of stifling calm. Unlike his kin, Acer remembers another life—one as a human in a different world -–complete with cravings for adventure, hearty meals, and the thrill of danger. Armed with his bow, spirit-blessed fruit, and centuries of skill, he abandons the sylvan idyll to carve out a new destiny beyond the forest. \n\n(Source: Titan Manga, edited)",
